## Future Features

### 1. Advanced Time Management (Pomodoro & Flow)
- Pomodoro Technique Integration (configurable work/break intervals).
- "Zen" or Focus Mode (minimalist, full-screen study view).

### 2. Gamification & Motivation
- Study Streaks (track consecutive days studied).
- Daily/Weekly Goals (set targets for hours or tasks completed).

### 3. Advanced Analytics & Insights
- Productivity Heatmaps (visualize most productive times of day/week).
- Subject Neglect Warnings (notify user of inactive subjects).

### 4. Enhanced Task & Session Organization
- Custom Session Tags (e.g., #reading, #review, #practice).
- Subtasks & Checklists (break down complex tasks).

### 5. Utilities
- Data Export/Backup (export to CSV/JSON).
- Quick Capture / Floating Widget (minimalist desktop timer/task entry).

